# splat-lab — Jetson Orin Nano Super + C615 → browser walkthrough

Frontier-2026 pipeline: live capture on a Logitech C615 USB webcam → Depth
Anything 3 Small for per-frame depth+poses+camera intrinsics → backproject to
a 3D Gaussian Splat PLY → SuperSplat Viewer (WebGPU, MIT) → browse on any
LAN device, with a separate **live RGB+depth+YOLO dashboard** for real-time
camera visibility.

**100% Apache-2.0 / MIT licensed.** Commercial-clean.

